RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: rvt_esri_multihillshade
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: RVT Multiple directions hillshade. Calculates hillshade in multiple directions.
RasterFunctionTemplate.Help: Analytical hillshading can be calculated in multiple directions that are equally distributed between 0° and 360° (Hobbs 1999). 0° is always in band 1, followed by azimuths in clockwise direction, e.g. 45° in band 2, 90° in band 3 … 315° in band 8, for calculation in 8 directions.
